data.description: MULTIPLE OFFERS- Highest/Best by 4/25 by 5pmIntroducing 434 SW 27th Ave, Delray Beach  located just 2 miles from thriving downtown Atlantic Ave, beaches, and restaurants. This tastefully remodeled townhouse comes with all the bells and whistles. The townhouse has 2 bedrooms 2 bathrooms and a 1 car garage, and is 1369 square feet under air. When you want to relax, walk into the backyard, and enjoy the sounds of the outdoor fountain and birds chirping.  WoodLake is an ALL AGES neighborhood offering a community pool, fitness center, tennis, pickleball, clubhouse, and basketball court. The low HOA fee includes cable, internet, and front yard mowing. A pet friendly community, which allows up to 2 pets. You are allowed to rent the unit after owning for 2 years.
